Looks, like we'll need to drop support of arrays or objects as keys due to JavaScript limitations:

```
> var obj = {};
undefined
> var arr = [1,2,3];
undefined
> var alt = {foo:'bar'};
undefined
> obj[arr] = true;
true
> obj[alt] = true;
true
> obj
{ '1,2,3': true,
  '[object Object]': true }
```

